<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.10">
<l>maṉṉu maturai vacutēvar vāḻmutalai</l>
<l>naṉṉaṟai yūrniṉ ṟanampiyai vampaviḻtār</l>
<l>kaṉṉavilun tōḷāṉ kaliya ṉolivallār</l>
<l>poṉṉulakil vāṉavarkkup puttēḷi rākuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the words of Kaliyaṉ, the one with boulder-like arms,</l>
<l>With a garland where fragrance wafts, about the noble</l>
<l rend="indent">who stands in virtuous Naṟaiyūr,</l>
<l>The primary reason for Vasudeva’s life in everlasting Mathurā,</l>
<l>They will be deities to the celestials in the golden land.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
